rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘大學站隔離係乜春都無，如果比狗係個到埋伏，義士預要係中大訓一晚都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHb7Shx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHb7Shx.png&h=606ff586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ff32dfd1f5f023df4b19bd5e447e99d600534b9","tid":1434250,"uid":11935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfae428cfff3ac52f96ee183c62903966796de76","tid":1434250,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37cdcb163a5ac0de3ae0d83a63e6d37b8778d73f","tid":1434250,"uid":293507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"睇到好灰, 走唔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"我由一個中立嘅角度諗大家可以點撤離<br />\n無錯條路係好離譜<br />\n不過已經係最佳路線"},{"pid":"ee3f0b746c94ba89bb6f8cd72848c5e6daf80965","tid":1434250,"uid":9548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:33:47.000Z","msg":"宜家收到既消息係肯定大部份藍絲舖頭應該唔開，我真係希望聽日乜事都冇發生，等班仆街蝕左一日生意額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce65cf1978d4b4680f9747e30ec06d8bb3b33f8","tid":1434250,"uid":220766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:44:05.000Z","msg":"點解淨係諗向南走<br />\n向北走都得<br />\n帝欣-&gt; 康樂園-&gt;南華莆 有巴士入粉嶺<br />\n再唔係行路去粉嶺實輕鬆過去大學"},{"pid":"626a93448611972acf17caf82b2ecd150556d0c2","tid":1434250,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXJVgmk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXJVgmk.png&h=9b18697c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nfrom隔離post<br />\n太和方向有上水ptu總部支援<br />\n想係海濱方向搭車會穿過警察防線<br />\n<br />\n可以預計會比人兩邊夾<br />\n咁有兩條路走<br />\n太和火車站和富亨<br />\n<br />\n係太和搭特別車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或<br />\n係太和搭特別車去大埔火車站<br />\n然後繞過警察防線去海濱上巴士<br />\n<br />\n上太和火車兩個方法都係九死一生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上富亨總站<br />\n無錯，地理上富亨係個死位<br />\n不過而家巴士上車點係富亨就係另一回事<br />\n政府張meno整到大部份南行線都係富亨開<br />\n想搭巴士就唯有去果邊<br />\n<br />\n但出入富亨嘅馬路得兩條，一封左就完全出唔到車<br />\n黑警會唔會引你地去搭車然後封尻住條路呢？咁真係要入屋或上山啦，無路走<br />\n自行判斷風險"},{"pid":"ceb15b94c0606fc7681c8ee225bf3cb37de807fb","tid":1434250,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ce65cf1978d4b4680f9747e30ec06d8bb3b33f8","tid":1434250,"uid":220766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:44:05.000Z","msg":"點解淨係諗向南走<br />\n向北走都得<br />\n帝欣-&gt; 康樂園-&gt;南華莆 有巴士入粉嶺<br />\n再唔係行路去粉嶺實輕鬆過去大學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:58:36.000Z","msg":"畫條路線出黎討論下"},{"pid":"e2eb6cb997a6f3d1a6dd027379c47b5e5b4c7400","tid":1434250,"uid":124071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ce65cf1978d4b4680f9747e30ec06d8bb3b33f8","tid":1434250,"uid":220766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:44:05.000Z","msg":"點解淨係諗向南走<br />\n向北走都得<br />\n帝欣-&gt; 康樂園-&gt;南華莆 有巴士入粉嶺<br />\n再唔係行路去粉嶺實輕鬆過去大學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"冇錯...喺帝欣一直跟住單車徑行就會入到粉嶺。5KM左右"},{"pid":"e726ff453c62ce287e7a93903c416f63b18ebf5f","tid":1434250,"uid":9548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"我要強調係成個新界北既警力，你地諗到既路線我覺得都已經有晒部署"},{"pid":"5a8241ccf4a96a18c781e0af0e19f39f247cf7d3","tid":1434250,"uid":11935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7244ee2a17cf47e0add1f1a97aae84c8051cf647","tid":1434250,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc